OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782847100
OL,3,CMarket in Sheffield closes after pests
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,FA popular market in Sheffield has
OL,7,Ftemporarily closed after pests were
OL,8,Ffound.
OL,10,FMoor Market, in the city centre, is
OL,11,Fhome to more than 90 independent
OL,12,Ftraders.
OL,14,FIt was shut on the evening of Friday
OL,15,F26 June and will be across the weekend.
OL,17,FOfficials cannot confirm when the
OL,18,Fmarket will reopen.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
