CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782847100
OL,3,CMarket in Sheffield closes after pests
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,FRichard Eyre, Director of Street Scene
OL,7,Fand Regulations at Sheffield City
OL,8,FCouncil, said it was necessary after
OL,9,F"the identification of a pest issue
OL,10,Faffecting parts of the market,
OL,11,Fincluding some food businesses.
OL,13,F"The Council has taken the decision to
OL,14,Fclose the market immediately so that
OL,15,Furgent action can be taken to protect
OL,16,Fpublic health and stop the issue from
OL,17,Fspreading further.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
