FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782847100
OL,3,CMarket in Sheffield closes after pests
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,F"While the issue has been identified
OL,7,Fin specific areas, closing the whole
OL,8,Fmarket is a precautionary but
OL,9,Fnecessary step.
OL,11,F"It enables a full and coordinated
OL,12,Fprogramme of treatment and deep
OL,13,Fcleaning to be carried out across all
OL,14,Funits, communal areas and supporting
OL,15,Fspaces such as storage, significantly
OL,16,Freducing the risk of the problem
OL,17,Fspreading.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
