FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782847100
OL,3,CMarket in Sheffield closes after pests
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,F"Acting quickly is particularly
OL,7,Fimportant given the current period of
OL,8,Fextreme heat due to unprecedented
OL,9,Fweather, which creates conditions
OL,10,Fwhere pests can spread more rapidly.
OL,12,F"Taking decisive action now is the
OL,13,Fmost effective way to contain the
OL,14,Fissue and protect both businesses and
OL,15,Fthe public."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
